<section class="section" id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title animate-on-scroll">Contacto</h2>
    <div class="contact-content">
      <p class="contact-text animate-on-scroll" data-delay="1">
        ¿Tienes un proyecto en mente o quieres colaborar? Estoy abierto a nuevas oportunidades.
        No dudes en enviarme un mensaje.
      </p>
      <div class="contact-links stagger-children">
        <a href="mailto:tu@email.com" class="contact-item">
          <span class="contact-icon">✉</span>
          tu@email.com
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/tuusuario" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <span class="contact-icon">&#60;/&#62;</span>
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/tuusuario" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="contact-item">
          <span class="contact-icon">in</span>
          LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-content {
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-text {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
  }

  .contact-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
    transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.02);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
  }

  .contact-icon {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
</style>
